Script to use remote slicer via ssh.

Needed:
* Conection whithout password (RSA)
* Configure pronterface/pronsole to use the script as slicer: [path to script]/remote_slice.sh $s $o
* Must be a folder $HOME/stl in the remote machine
* Must be skeinforge folder in /opt/ in the remote machine
* The asimov repository must be in /home in the local machine
* In order to have parameter completion append the file dot-bash_completion to ~/.bash_completion
